{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"8dizeij41ps6wt16a6r8k8p","title":"Async Await","desc":"","updated":1664357621249,"created":1664305287465,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.async-await","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"bf744f6de2546e60db11518d41c16f55","links":[],"anchors":{"asyncawait-primer":{"type":"header","text":"Async/.await Primer","value":"asyncawait-primer","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"why":{"type":"header","text":"Why?","value":"why","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"what":{"type":"header","text":"What?","value":"what","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"how":{"type":"header","text":"How?","value":"how","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"d81qplbgwaiawwudxe38xpf","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"async-await\">Async Await<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#async-await\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"asyncawait-primer\">Async/.await Primer<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#asyncawait-primer\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://rust-lang.github.io/async-book/01_getting_started/04_async_await_primer.html\">https://rust-lang.github.io/async-book/01_getting_started/04_async_await_primer.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"why\">Why?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#why\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Run multiple asynchronous functions</li>\n<li>Sync between them using .await </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"what\">What?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#what\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in tool for writng asynchronous functions</li>\n<li>async:\n<ul>\n<li>A block of code -> a state machine (implements <code>Future trait</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Blocked <code>Future</code> will yeild control of the thread, allowing other <code>Future</code> to run\n<code>Future</code> acts as a interupt whenever a determined event is received -> able to run multiple <code>Future</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><code>Future</code> needs to be run on an executor</strong>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"how\">How?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#how\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>dependencies: Cargo.toml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-toml\"><code class=\"language-toml\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">dependencies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">futures</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0.3\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create an asynchronous function</p>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">do_sth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Returned a <code>Future</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Runs <strong>async fn</strong> on an executor</p>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token comment\">/*\nblocks the current thread until the provided future has run to completion\n*/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">futures<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span>executor<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span></span>block_on<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">hello_world</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token macro property\">println!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> future <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello_world</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// assign a function</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">block_on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>future<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// runs future</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>using <code>.await</code> to wait for the <code>Future</code> trait</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>waits for the <code>future</code> to complete</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>allows other tasks to run if the future is currently unable to make progress</p>\n<pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\"><span class=\"token comment\">// dance can be executed at the same time as learn &#x26; sing song</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// sing_song must wait for learn_song to complete</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">learn_song</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">-></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Song</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/**/</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">sing_song</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>song<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Song</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/**/</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">dance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/**/</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">learn_and_sing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// using block_on blocks an entire thread</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> song <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">learn_song</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">sing_song</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>song<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">async_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> f1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">learn_and_sing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> f2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">dance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token comment\">// join! waits for multiple futures concurrently</span>\n    <span class=\"token namespace\">futures<span class=\"token punctuation\">::</span></span><span class=\"token macro property\">join!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>f1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> f2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">block_on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">async_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[